org.apache.ctakes.core.cc.pretty.cell

Interface ItemCell

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BaseItemCell, UmlsItemCell
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractItemCell, DefaultBaseItemCell, DefaultUmlsItemCell, EventCell, TimexCell

    public interface ItemCell
    Container class for information about an item (text, annotation, etc.) cell - used for calculating print layout.
